  <!-- Testimonials Widget *********** -->

  <Testimonials
    title="Client testimonials"
    subtitle="Discover what clients have to say about their experiences working with us."
    testimonials={[
      {
        testimonial: `Solution Planets has been an excellent web product development partner, having worked closely with them on four different projects. They have almost always managed timely delivery of milestones as per agreed schedule. The experience of people I've referred them to has also been good - the best indicator of which is their repeat orders.`,
        name: 'Rajesh Haldipur',
        job: 'Former Head, Tax and Regulatory services',
        image: {
          src: '~/assets/images/dp/dp1.png',
          alt: 'DP Image',
        },
      },
      {
        testimonial: `We are really happy with the service provided by Dharmesh bhai and his team at Solution Planets! They go out of their way to help clients with their tech needs and are very sharp when it comes to understanding & conceptualising what exactly a client wants in a product from a technology perspective! Also, hands down, they are the most reliable tech partners I have ever worked with! Kudos to their entire team!`,
        name: 'Tanaya Doshi',
        job: 'VP Strategy - Realtime Taxsutra Services',
        image: {
          src: '~/assets/images/dp/dp2.png',
          alt: 'DP Image',
        },
      },
      {
        testimonial: `We have been associated with Solution Planets for more than a decade. We are very much satisfied and happy with their services and relationship. In fact we are now a family. I wish people get associated with them and can enjoy the long lasting business partnership with them.`,
        name: 'Pankaj Sanghavi',
        job: 'Chartered Acountant',
        image: {
          src: '~/assets/images/dp/dp3.png',
          alt: 'DP Image',
        },        
      },
      {
        testimonial: `Team at Solution Planets, are people with on-ground reality; understanding client perspectives, being adaptable with quick responses, and setting realistic expectations. It has helped us in building our back office operations per our requirement! Thank You.`,
        name: 'Amit Doshi',
        job: 'Investment Director, Care Portfolio Managers',
        image: {
          src: '~/assets/images/dp/dp4.png',
          alt: 'DP Image',
        },
      },
      {
        testimonial: `We have contracted Solutions Planet to develop various software for us over the past years, and we have been more than satisfied with their performance. Their understanding the client requirements, implicating those in development and giving user friendly application is standing them out from others. Their work has always been professional and accurate. We will not hesitate to utilize their services in our future project.`,
        name: 'Bharat Jagnani',
        job: 'QESS India',
        image: {
          src: '~/assets/images/dp/dp5.png',
          alt: 'DP Imagee',
        },
      },
      {
        testimonial: `During lockdown, we shifted our mail from our in-house dedicated mail server to Microsoft. Dharmeshbhai and his team made sure of a seamless experience, minimum downtime and also helped us retain and access our old email data easily. The team also helped us taking our data to cloud from local storage and raised our queries with Microsoft personnel on our behalf. There is a visible improvement in our communication and productivity.`,
        name: 'Siddharth Zaveri',
        job: 'Director, Mahavir Hydraulics Pvt Ltd',
        image: {
          src: '~/assets/images/dp/dp6.png',
          alt: 'DP Image',
        },
      },
    ]}
  />

